WEBVTT

00:04:59.514 --> 00:05:00.786
the one joy she had:

00:05:01.433 --> 00:05:02.583
to wear color.

00:05:04.129 --> 00:05:05.983
In India, according to custom,

00:05:06.007 --> 00:05:08.283
when a Hindu woman becomes a widow,

00:05:08.307 --> 00:05:11.002
all she's allowed to wear is white

00:05:11.026 --> 00:05:13.104
from the day of the death of her husband.

00:05:13.634 --> 00:05:15.771
No one made my grandmother wear white.

00:05:16.424 --> 00:05:20.259
However, every woman she'd known
who had outlived her husband,

00:05:20.283 --> 00:05:21.866
including her mother,

00:05:21.890 --> 00:05:23.040
had done it.

00:05:23.463 --> 00:05:27.847
This oppression was so internalized,

00:05:27.871 --> 00:05:29.468
so deep-rooted,

00:05:29.492 --> 00:05:32.135
that she herself refused a choice.